Public Sub S_BuKaS()
On Error GoTo KoErr
'Speichert einen Kassenbestand

Dim IdBnk As Long
Dim NeuDa As Date
Dim NeuZe As Date
Dim BuJah As String
Dim GeSum As Double
Dim SaEin As Double
Dim SaAus As Double
Dim SaBan As Double
Dim GesZa As Integer
